    },
    {
      '@type': 'Question',
      name: 'When should I take glutamine gummies?',
      acceptedAnswer: { '@type': 'Answer', text: 'For gut health: take glutamine gummies first thing in the morning on an empty stomach to maximize delivery to intestinal cells. For muscle recovery: take within 30 minutes after exercise when intramuscular glutamine is depleted. For immune support: split doses between morning and evening for sustained blood glutamine levels. For general wellness: timing is less critical — consistency of daily intake matters more than specific timing. Glutamine can be taken with or without food, though empty-stomach dosing maximizes intestinal absorption for gut health purposes.' },
    },
